<view class="content"><input type="text" placeholder="邮箱" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['','email','$event',[]]]]]]}}" value="{{email}}" onInput="__e"/><view class="tips" style="color:red;">{{"上次发送的验证码："+code}}</view><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['setVerifyCode',['login']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">设置验证码（注册&登录）</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['loginByEmail',['$event']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">邮箱验证码登录（不存在则注册）</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['setVerifyCode',['bind']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">设置验证码（绑定邮箱）</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['bindEmail',['$event']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">绑定邮箱</button><view class="tips">绑定邮箱时如果不传验证码或者传空则直接绑定并设置email_confirmed为1，不会去校验验证码</view><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['setVerifyCode',['unbind']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">设置验证码（解绑邮箱）</button><button type="default" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['unbindEmail',['$event']]]]]}}" onTap="__e">解绑邮箱</button><view class="tips">解绑邮箱时如果不传验证码或者传空则直接解除绑定绑定，不会去校验验证码</view></view>